snippet.title: Monster Hunter Generations - Opening Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
The Fated Four are unleashed on July 15! Assemble your party and prepare for a hunt for the ages.  
 
Monster Hunter Generations will be available on July 15 on the Nintendo 3DS.

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
